                            </p>
                            <h4>About the project Asure Network:</h4>
                            <p>
                                Asure Network is a layer 2 scaling network that enables fast, easy and secure
                                transactions for not only payment transactions, but also generalized smart contracts.
                                Founded by German insurance and technology experts, the network enables everyone to
                                quickly build, operate, and use highly scalable business applications through
                                innovations in multi-chain scaling techniques and incentive-aligned crypto economics
                                mechanisms.
                            </p>
                            <h4>What problems does Asure Network solve?</h4>
                            <p>
                                We are developing Asure Network as an infrastructure for Social Security systems of the
                                future. Our goal is to provide access to such systems for individuals as well as to
                                offer such decentralized systems to governments.
                                The existing social security systems are based on centralized databases and crooked
                                processes allowing fraud and corruption. Labor-intensive processes and lack of trust in
                                systems are the challenges we solve with the help of blockchain.
                                We are working on the solution that allows global inclusion in the social security
                                market, just as Bitcoin allows for global inclusion in the financial market.

                            </p>
                            <h4>Where do the requirements for the Asure Network come from?</h4>
                            <p>
                                We have developed several prototypes of decentralized pension/insurance models to see
                                how decentralized Social Security systems can be designed with people in mind.
                                The prototypes are based on the German statutory pension system. We obtained very
                                valuable feedback after modelling different use-cases in a workshop for the German
                                Pension Insurance Association (Deutsche Rentenversicherung Bund).
                                The insights that we obtained helped us design Asure Network to provide an optimal
                                blockchain infrastructure for the future social security services such as transparent,
                                scalable and compliant with the data protection policies Pension and Insurance systems
                                as well as systems for enabling Basic Income solutions.
                            </p>

                            <h4>Our Mission:</h4>
                            <p>
                                To help the social security achieve the necessary standards of quality, transparency,
                                and reliability.
                            </p>
                            <h4>Our Vision:</h4>
                            <p>
                                People around the world enjoy their lives without having to worry about any risks or
                                losses.
                            </p>
